        "subject": "LU-7706 tests: add dmesg -c to conf-sanity_83",
        "message": "LU-7706 tests: add dmesg -c to conf-sanity_83\n\nDmesg clearing is needed because previous tests\n(for example conf-sanity_62) may also be the results\nof message \"VFS: Busy inodes after unmount of ...\".\nRemove duble $dev after mkfs ... --reformat.\n\nChange-Id: I2accc3ea805ed96a152510d97f6001df1b6d5bd8\nSigned-off-by: Sergey Cheremencev <sergey.cheremencev@seagate.com>\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-2109\n"
